{
  "video_id": "W1KIgMXPR28",
  "title": "Boniface Mwangi: The day I stood up alone",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13707.0,
      "end_time": 16596.0,
      "text": "People back home call me a heckler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16596.0,
      "end_time": 19313.0,
      "text": "a troublemaker, an irritant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19313.0,
      "end_time": 21982.0,
      "text": "a rebel, an activist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21983.0,
      "end_time": 23840.0,
      "text": "the voice of the people."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23840.0,
      "end_time": 26900.0,
      "text": "But that wasn&#39;t always me."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26650.0,
      "end_time": 28182.0,
      "text": "Growing up, I had a nickname."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28182.0,
      "end_time": 30502.0,
      "text": "They used to call me Softy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30502.0,
      "end_time": 33754.0,
      "text": "meaning the soft, harmless boy."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33755.0,
      "end_time": 36495.0,
      "text": "Like every other human being, I avoided trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36495.0,
      "end_time": 38538.0,
      "text": "In my childhood, they taught me silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38538.0,
      "end_time": 40339.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t argue, do as you&#39;re told."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40340.0,
      "end_time": 44272.0,
      "text": "In Sunday school, they taught me don&#39;t confront, don&#39;t argue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44272.0,
      "end_time": 47585.0,
      "text": "even if you&#39;re right, turn the other cheek."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47585.0,
      "end_time": 52182.0,
      "text": "This was reinforced by the political climate of the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52182.0,
      "end_time": 55783.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55783.0,
      "end_time": 57592.0,
      "text": "Kenya is a country where you are guilty"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57592.0,
      "end_time": 60239.0,
      "text": "until proven rich."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60239.0,
      "end_time": 62983.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62984.0,
      "end_time": 65726.0,
      "text": "Kenya&#39;s poor are five times more likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65726.0,
      "end_time": 68650.0,
      "text": "to be shot dead by the police who are meant to protect them"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68650.0,
      "end_time": 70298.0,
      "text": "than by criminals."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70298.0,
      "end_time": 72945.0,
      "text": "This was reinforced by the political climate of the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72945.0,
      "end_time": 75893.0,
      "text": "We had a president, Moi, who was a dictator."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75894.0,
      "end_time": 78100.0,
      "text": "He ruled the country with an iron fist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78100.0,
      "end_time": 80538.0,
      "text": "and anyone who dared question his authority"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80538.0,
      "end_time": 85506.0,
      "text": "was arrested, tortured, jailed or even killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85507.0,
      "end_time": 89431.0,
      "text": "That meant that people were taught to be smart cowards, stay out of trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89431.0,
      "end_time": 91474.0,
      "text": "Being a coward was not an insult."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91474.0,
      "end_time": 93401.0,
      "text": "Being a coward was a compliment."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93401.0,
      "end_time": 96559.0,
      "text": "We used to be told that a coward goes home to his mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96559.0,
      "end_time": 100320.0,
      "text": "What that meant: that if you stayed out of trouble you&#39;re going to stay alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100320.0,
      "end_time": 102259.0,
      "text": "I used to question this advice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 105820.0,
      "text": "and eight years ago we had an election in Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105820.0,
      "end_time": 107565.0,
      "text": "and the results were violently disputed."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107565.0,
      "end_time": 112301.0,
      "text": "What followed that election was terrible violence, rape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112302.0,
      "end_time": 116239.0,
      "text": "and the killing of over 1,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116239.0,
      "end_time": 119360.0,
      "text": "My work was to document the violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 119360.0,
      "end_time": 122216.0,
      "text": "As a photographer, I took thousands of images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122216.0,
      "end_time": 124282.0,
      "text": "and after two months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124283.0,
      "end_time": 129158.0,
      "text": "the two politicians came together, had a cup of tea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129157.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132595.0,
      "text": "signed a peace agreement, and the country moved on."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132595.0,
      "end_time": 136124.0,
      "text": "I was a very disturbed man because I saw the violence firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136124.0,
      "end_time": 139730.0,
      "text": "I saw the killings. I saw the displacement."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139730.0,
      "end_time": 142810.0,
      "text": "I met women who had been raped, and it disturbed me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 142811.0,
      "end_time": 144855.0,
      "text": "but the country never spoke about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144855.0,
      "end_time": 147339.0,
      "text": "We pretended. We all became smart cowards."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147339.0,
      "end_time": 150938.0,
      "text": "We decided to stay out of trouble and not talk about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150938.0,
      "end_time": 154234.0,
      "text": "Ten months later, I quit my job. I said I could not stand it anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154235.0,
      "end_time": 156830.0,
      "text": "After quitting my job, I decided to organize my friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156830.0,
      "end_time": 158850.0,
      "text": "to speak about the violence in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 158850.0,
      "end_time": 160714.0,
      "text": "to speak about the state of the nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160714.0,
      "end_time": 164829.0,
      "text": "and June 1, 2009 was the day that we were meant to go to the stadium"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164830.0,
      "end_time": 166889.0,
      "text": "and try and get the president&#39;s attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 166889.0,
      "end_time": 168329.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a national holiday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 168329.0,
      "end_time": 169978.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s broadcast across the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169978.0,
      "end_time": 173386.0,
      "text": "and I showed up at the stadium."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 173386.0,
      "end_time": 176380.0,
      "text": "My friends did not show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 176380.0,
      "end_time": 179753.0,
      "text": "I found myself alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 179753.0,
      "end_time": 182279.0,
      "text": "and I didn&#39;t know what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182280.0,
      "end_time": 183695.0,
      "text": "I was scared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183695.0,
      "end_time": 185864.0,
      "text": "but I knew very well that that particular day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185865.0,
      "end_time": 187860.0,
      "text": "I had to make a decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 187860.0,
      "end_time": 189509.0,
      "text": "Was I able to live as a coward, like everyone else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189509.0,
      "end_time": 191107.0,
      "text": "or was I going to make a stand?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191107.0,
      "end_time": 193313.0,
      "text": "And when the president stood up to speak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193313.0,
      "end_time": 197920.0,
      "text": "I found myself on my feet shouting at the president,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 197920.0,
      "end_time": 201113.0,
      "text": "telling him to remember the post-election violence victims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201114.0,
      "end_time": 203390.0,
      "text": "to stop the corruption."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203390.0,
      "end_time": 205595.0,
      "text": "And suddenly, out of nowhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 205595.0,
      "end_time": 208707.0,
      "text": "the police pounced on me like hungry lions."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 208707.0,
      "end_time": 210564.0,
      "text": "They held my mouth"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 210564.0,
      "end_time": 212491.0,
      "text": "and dragged me out of the stadium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 212491.0,
      "end_time": 215462.0,
      "text": "where they thoroughly beat me up and locked me up in jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217112.0,
      "end_time": 223870.0,
      "text": "I spent that night in a cold cement floor in the jail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 223870.0,
      "end_time": 226518.0,
      "text": "and that got me thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 226518.0,
      "end_time": 228389.0,
      "text": "What was making me feel this way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228389.0,
      "end_time": 231554.0,
      "text": "My friends and family thought I was crazy because of what I did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 231554.0,
      "end_time": 236568.0,
      "text": "and the images that I took were disturbing my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236568.0,
      "end_time": 239518.0,
      "text": "The images that I took were just a number to many Kenyans."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 239518.0,
      "end_time": 241465.0,
      "text": "Most Kenyans did not see the violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 241465.0,
      "end_time": 243160.0,
      "text": "It was a story to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 243160.0,
      "end_time": 245947.0,
      "text": "And so I decided to actually start a street exhibition"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245947.0,
      "end_time": 248733.0,
      "text": "to show the images of the violence across the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 248733.0,
      "end_time": 250707.0,
      "text": "and get people talking about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250707.0,
      "end_time": 253516.0,
      "text": "We traveled the country and showed the images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253516.0,
      "end_time": 256998.0,
      "text": "and this was a journey that has started me to the activist path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 256999.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259716.00000000003,
      "text": "where I decided to become silent no more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 259716.0,
      "end_time": 261914.0,
      "text": "to talk about those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 261914.0,
      "end_time": 265563.0,
      "text": "We traveled, and our general site from our street exhibit"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265564.0,
      "end_time": 270362.0,
      "text": "became for political graffiti about the situation in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270362.0,
      "end_time": 273120.0,
      "text": "talking about corruption, bad leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 273120.0,
      "end_time": 276900.0,
      "text": "We have even done symbolic burials."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 276900.0,
      "end_time": 280882.0,
      "text": "We have delivered live pigs to Kenya&#39;s parliament"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280882.0,
      "end_time": 282810.0,
      "text": "as a symbol of our politicians&#39; greed."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 282810.0,
      "end_time": 285410.0,
      "text": "It has been done in Uganda and other countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 285410.0,
      "end_time": 288550.0,
      "text": "and what is most powerful is that the images have been picked by the media"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288550.0,
      "end_time": 291586.0,
      "text": "and amplified across the country, across the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 291586.0,
      "end_time": 294233.0,
      "text": "Where I used to stand up alone seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 294233.0,
      "end_time": 297259.0,
      "text": "now I belong to a community of many people who stand up with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297259.0,
      "end_time": 301587.0,
      "text": "I am no longer alone when I stand up to speak about these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 302177.0,
      "end_time": 306350.0,
      "text": "I belong to a group of young people who are passionate about the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 306350.0,
      "end_time": 308200.0,
      "text": "who want to bring about change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 308200.0,
      "end_time": 312614.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re no longer afraid, and they&#39;re no longer smart cowards."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 313744.0,
      "end_time": 316472.0,
      "text": "So that was my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318242.0,
      "end_time": 320840.0,
      "text": "That day in the stadium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 320840.0,
      "end_time": 323327.0,
      "text": "I stood up as a smart coward."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323327.0,
      "end_time": 328574.0,
      "text": "By that one action, I said goodbye to the 24 years living as a coward."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 328574.0,
      "end_time": 331616.0,
      "text": "There are two most powerful days in your life:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 331616.0,
      "end_time": 336162.0,
      "text": "the day you&#39;re born, and the day you discover why."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 336771.0,
      "end_time": 340150.0,
      "text": "That day standing up in that stadium shouting at the President,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 340150.0,
      "end_time": 343294.0,
      "text": "I discovered why I was truly born,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343295.0,
      "end_time": 346546.0,
      "text": "that I would no longer be silent in the face of injustice."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 347776.0,
      "end_time": 350580.0,
      "text": "Do you know why you were born?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 351700.0,
      "end_time": 353534.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 353535.0,
      "end_time": 358454.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 360524.0,
      "end_time": 363310.0,
      "text": "Tom Rielly: It&#39;s an amazing story."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 363310.0,
      "end_time": 365587.0,
      "text": "I just want to ask you a couple quick questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 365587.0,
      "end_time": 367907.0,
      "text": "So PAWA254:"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 367907.0,
      "end_time": 372219.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve created a studio, a place where young people can go"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 372220.0,
      "end_time": 374176.0,
      "text": "and harness the power of digital media"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 374176.0,
      "end_time": 376687.0,
      "text": "to do some of this action."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 376687.0,
      "end_time": 378564.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s happening now with PAWA?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 378564.0,
      "end_time": 381347.0,
      "text": "Boniface Mwangi: So we have  this community of filmmakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 381347.0,
      "end_time": 384710.0,
      "text": "graffiti artists, musicians, and when there&#39;s an issue in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 384710.0,
      "end_time": 387510.0,
      "text": "we come together, we brainstorm, and take up on that issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 387511.0,
      "end_time": 389567.0,
      "text": "So our most powerful tool is art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 389567.0,
      "end_time": 393398.0,
      "text": "because we live in a very busy world where people are so busy in their life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 393398.0,
      "end_time": 395465.0,
      "text": "and they don&#39;t have time to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 395465.0,
      "end_time": 399597.0,
      "text": "So we package our activism and we package our message in art."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 399598.0,
      "end_time": 404577.0,
      "text": "So from the music, the graffiti,  the art, that&#39;s what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405557.0,
      "end_time": 407585.0,
      "text": "Can I say one more thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 407585.0,
      "end_time": 409465.0,
      "text": "TR: Yeah, of course. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 409466.0,
      "end_time": 412101.0,
      "text": "BM: In spite of being arrested, beaten up, threatened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 412101.0,
      "end_time": 413814.0,
      "text": "the moment I discovered my voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 413814.0,
      "end_time": 416710.0,
      "text": "that I could actually stand up for what I really believed in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 416710.0,
      "end_time": 417748.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m no longer afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 417748.0,
      "end_time": 420490.0,
      "text": "I used to be called softy, but I&#39;m no longer softy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 420490.0,
      "end_time": 423891.0,
      "text": "because I discovered who I really am, as in, that&#39;s what I want to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 423891.0,
      "end_time": 426927.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s such beauty in doing that."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 426927.0,
      "end_time": 430316.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nothing as powerful as that, knowing that I&#39;m meant to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 430316.0,
      "end_time": 433462.0,
      "text": "because you don&#39;t get scared, you just continue living your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 433463.0,
      "end_time": 435649.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 435649.0,
